            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px;">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-3">
            <p style="font-weight: bold;">All registration types include admission to the followings:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>•	All technical sessions</li>
                <li>•	Coffee breaks</li>
                <li>•	Lunches</li>
                <li>•	Academic tour</li>
                <li>•	Gala dinner </li>
                <li>•	Certificate of Attendance</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px;">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-3">
            <p style="font-weight: bold;">FCETC 2025 Registration Policy</p>
            <ul>
                <li>-	Onsite registration is not available for all types of participants. Registration is only accepted with online registration and payment. Please finish your registration and payment before the deadline. </li>
                <li>-	The registration fees apply for a maximum of 7000 words only, including all figures, tables, references and appendix.  </li>
                <li>-	Co-author who wants to attend the conference is advised to register well in advance. Conference certificate is only offered to the main author who is in charge of paper presentation at the conference. </li>
                <li>-	Payment must be paid in VND only. </li>
                <li>-   Please upload the required documents to the online registration system or conference email box: <a href="mailto:fcetc@fe.edu.vn">FCETC@fe.edu.vn</a> to finish the registration:</li>
                <li>•	Full paper</li>
                <li>•	Presentation slides</li>
                <li>•	Payment proof</li>

            </ul>

        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px;">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-3">
            <p style="font-weight: bold;">Cancellation and Refund Policy</p>
            <p>Registration cannot be cancelled and payment will not be refunded by any cases</p>
            <p>Once receive a notification from FCETC 2025 that the paper is accepted, please follow the steps below:</p>
            <p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Fill online registration form for each paper (Only applied for <strong>ONE</strong> author only)</p>
            <p><strong>Step 2: </strong>Pay registration fee</p>
            <p>Once finish online registration, please pay the registration fee via bank transfer by <strong>July 15th, 2025</strong></p>
            <p>The bank account is detailed as follows:</p>
            <p>Our Bank  Name: TIEN PHONG COMMERCIAL JOINT STOCK BANK, HANOI, VIETNAM </p>
            <p>Our Account No.: xxxxxxx</p>
            <p>Swift Code: TPBVVNVX </p>
            <p>Beneficiary: Truong Dai Hoc FPT</p>
            <p>Address: xxxxxx</p>
            <p>* Bank Address or Bank Branch is only compulsory for domestic transfer. International author or listener do NOT have to insert this information during their international money order (IMO)</p>
            <p>Transfer content: Please STRICTLY follow the following formula:</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold;">FCETC 2025 – PaperID1_PaperID2_PaperIDn – Full name of the author – Type – Region</p>
            <p><i>Example: Author <strong>Van A Nguyen</strong> pays for <strong>02 accepted papers</strong> with IDs: 1234 and 5678 will conduct payment transfer with the following content: </i></p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold;"><i>FCETC 2025 – 1234_5678 – Van A Nguyen – Regular – Vietnam</i></p>
            <p><strong>Step 3: </strong>Prepare the camera-ready package and the scanned copyright then send it to the organizer’s email address: <a href="mailto:fcetc@fe.edu.vn">fcetc@fe.edu.vn</a> (an email for each accepted paper) as follows: [FCETC 2025] - Paper ID – Camera-ready and Copyrights</p>
        </div>

    </div>
